Ing '''De La Salle Philippines, Inc.''' ('''DLSP''' or '''DLSPI''') ing lupung talapanibala (governing body) da reng eganaganang [[w:De La Salle Brothers in the Philippines|Lasallian]] a pipagaralang pang-distritu king [[Filipinas]]. Iti ing tatalan kareng labing walung campus a magsarili (autonomous) king mabilug a bangsa. Mitatag ya kanitang [[2006]] antimong kayalili ning '''De La Salle University System''', metung a [[w:university system]] a bibilugan da reng walung campus a magsarili king [[Metro Manila]] ampo reng kasiping nang lalawigan a Laguna ampong Cavite a mitatag lalam ning pamanungkulan nang [[w:Andrew Gonzalez|Bro. Andrew Gonzalez FSC]] antimong pakibat king masalusung pamandagul da reng pipagaralan a Lasallian ba lang magamit king makayagpang diling paralan deng bandi (resources) da reti. Kanitang [[1911]] ya mitatag ing minuna nang campus, samantalang keta yang [[2006]] mibuklat ing bayung dili king [[Bagac]], [[Bataan]].   

Kapakayan ning DLSP ing papalyaryan ing matalab o efectivung pamanyuyu at sumaup a magtipid la reng labingwalung pipagaralan kapamilatan ning pamiugnayan a mas centralizadu o matigik. Mitatag ya ing National Mission Council (NMC) bang magsilbing matas diling lupung a gagawang patakaran ning DLSP. Adwa lang pulu't atlu (23) deng kayanib king NMC: labing lima kareng myayaliwang pipagaralan, at walu ibat kareng La Salle Christian Brothers. Manatili yang non-stock at non-profit ing DLSP. King salukuyan, ing pamuntuk ning  De La Salle University-Manila,  i Br. Armin Luistro FSC, ing magsilbing Chief Executive Officer (CEO) o manimunang manungkulan a talapagpaganap ning corporaciun. Mika sarili yang Chancellor ampong school board ing balang institucion a kayanib, at mika ganap yang pamagsarili (full autonomy) ba neng panibalan ing kayang institucion.

